quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  69,38,Fela uksimu bima tubsÄḟrune
  69,39,Ve ma la tubsÄḟrune
  69,40,ÄḞnnehu lekavlu resulin keriymin
  69,41,Ve ma huve bikavli ÅaÂṀÄḟrin kaliylen ma tuÂṀminune
  69,42,Ve la bilkavli kahinin kaliylen ma tezekkerune
  69,43,Tenziylun min rabbilÂṀalemiyne
  69,44,Velev tekavvele ÂṀaleyna baÂṀdalÂṀekaviyli
  69,45,Leehazna minhu bilyemiyni
  69,46,Summe lekataÂṀna minhulvetiyne
  69,47,Fema minkum min ehadin ÂṀanhu haciziyne
  69,48,Ve innehu letezkiretun lilmuttekÄḟyne
  69,49,Ve inna lenaÂṀlemu enne minkum mukezzibiyne
  69,50,Ve innehu lehasretun ÂṀalelkafiriyne
  69,51,Ve innehu lehakkulyakÄḟyni
  69,52,Fesebbih bismi rabbikelÂṀazÄḟymi